      h4 Body scrolling
      p Scrolling the <code>&lt;body&gt;</code> element is disabled when an offcanvas and its backdrop are visible. Use the <code>data-bs-scroll</code> attribute to enable <code>&lt;body&gt;</code> scrolling.

      .bd-example
