      h4 Dark offcanvas
      p Change the appearance of offcanvases with utilities to better match them to different contexts like dark navbars. Here we add <code>.text-bg-dark</code> to the <code>.offcanvas</code> and <code>.btn-close-white</code> to <code>.btn-close</code> for proper styling with a dark offcanvas. If you have dropdowns within, consider also adding <code>.dropdown-menu-dark</code> to <code>.dropdown-menu</code>.

      .bd-example
