      h4 Responsive
      p Responsive offcanvas classes hide content outside the viewport from a specified breakpoint and down. Above that breakpoint, the contents within will behave as usual. For example, <code>.offcanvas-lg</code> hides content in an offcanvas below the <code>lg</code> breakpoint, but shows the content above the <code>lg</code> breakpoint.

      .bd-example
