        li <code>.offcanvas-lg</code>
        li <code>.offcanvas-xl</code>
        li <code>.offcanvas-xxl</code>

      h4 Placement
      p There's no default placement for offcanvas components, so you must add one of the modifier classes below.

      ul
        li <code>.offcanvas-start</code> places offcanvas on the left of the viewport (shown above)
        li <code>.offcanvas-end</code> places offcanvas on the right of the viewport
        li <code>.offcanvas-top</code> places offcanvas on the top of the viewport
        li <code>.offcanvas-bottom</code> places offcanvas on the bottom of the viewport

